      "review_summary": "The PR adds a nested `__openclaw.inboundDecoration.bareBody` contract and routes transcript, prompt replay, memory export, CLI dedupe, session-log, and Control UI consumers through it with legacy sentinel fallback.\n\nPR surface: Source +251, Tests +491. Total +742 across 18 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. Source inspection shows current main still has literal sentinel stripping paths for user-role text, so a user-authored block matching those sentinels can follow the same cleanup path as host metadata; I did not run a live channel repro in this read-only review.",
